325
00:16:43,585 --> 00:16:44,670
[dengan gemetar] Mm-hmm.

326
00:16:46,463 --> 00:16:47,964
[dalam bahasa Inggris] Nanti aku jelaskan,

327
00:16:47,965 --> 00:16:51,884
