[mengerang]

395
00:19:55,402 --> 00:19:56,904
Saya sangat menyesal.

396
00:19:57,487 --> 00:19:58,779
Tidak apa-apa.

397
00:19:58,780 --> 00:20:01,700
Ugh, aku ingin
